{"tid":2392163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國BNO 安全檢查 你是否港共間諜（即公務員）及港共走狗（所有武裝部隊）","createTime":"2021-02-02T15:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T07:52:09.000Z","uid":33263,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"91f863c8a1213b3328bb0123923aa9203ee557f8","tid":2392163,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/143807737_5002147686493611_7724548837486563193_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=2yfkAz-jYXIAX8TWP7v&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-2.xx&amp;oh=f3d6f6fde01fec8663baf63c9c68d31b&amp;oe=603D1F24\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F143807737_5002147686493611_7724548837486563193_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D2yfkAz-jYXIAX8TWP7v%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-2.xx%26oh%3Df3d6f6fde01fec8663baf63c9c68d31b%26oe%3D603D1F24&h=af28c817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國政府推岀BNO 5+1 移民簽證，主持人楊樂笙睇過英國個申請網頁，發現佢哋嘅審批條件，似乎有心限制某一啲人去申請，例如係政府工作嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n申請表格會好直接咁問，有冇做過持械部隊？其中一個選項直接問有冇做過警察，之後又問有冇曾經幫過政府做嘢。咁都唔止，仲會問申請人有冇發表過極端言論去針對某啲人，甚至會有舉報熱線。所以今次英國移民政策看似寬鬆，實質暗藏玄機。"},{"pid":"5fbc023668fa3387b639a7abb59dcee0460ca505","tid":2392163,"uid":33263,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"請大家進行舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621ac6150d0cf3c820179f5d1628a69f9a40996e","tid":2392163,"uid":33263,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"國安法後 所有港共公務員都會視為中共間諜人員<br />\n全部都驅逐 唔會申請到bno Visa <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共曱甴 咪想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1300eafbe500a0d84c701f7c08c38c951590164","tid